O'Neal is a fan of the National Hockey League's New Jersey Devils, who play in his hometown of Newark, and has been seen at several games over the years.[296] On January 11, 2014, O'Neal performed the ceremonial first puck and drove a Zamboni for a game between the Devils and the Florida Panthers.[297] O'Neal is also a fan of English football club Northampton Town, and has posted videos of support to their official YouTube page.[298]
